Author: SemicolonButterfly
Text: Eh, I think hyperawareness of our bodies is often part of this shindig. I recognize a lot of my thoughts are obsessive/irrational/self-centered...but seeing that doesn't magically make the thoughts abate. (I wish)  I'm also a small A cup. Currently I wear sports bras basically 24 hours a day. I don't like feeling the movement or, like, accidentally brushing my upper arm against the curve, etc.
